channel.title: 2 Thieving Questions [Project Insanity] Rep++ For This One
channel.description:
1.) How can I change what stalls reward players when they thieve from them?
2.) How can I change the locations of the stalls? I tried looking in objectmanager.java, but I couldn't seem to find it.
Extra: Does anyone know how to change your combat level if you're an owner? For example, even though the max level on my server is 126, is there a way that I can make it 138 just for myself?
Thanks,
Anthony
